  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00943', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-110-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '若供給曲線為完全無彈性，下列何者正確？', '["政府無法有效進行價格管制", "廠商可以採取薄利多銷策略", "均衡價格完全由供給面決定", "供給者無法將從量稅轉嫁給需求者"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:19+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a995a09c8dd5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "214c7af8bde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "512", "s": "0505", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00944', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-110-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '咖啡價格在上個月大幅上漲，但銷售量維持不變。下面五人各提出一種解釋，誰可能是對的？ 阿甘：需求增加且供給完全無彈性。 阿國：需求增加且完全無彈性。 阿信：需求增加且供給同幅度減少。 阿妹：供給減少且需求具單位彈性。 阿強：供給減少且需求完全無彈性。', '["阿甘、阿國和阿信", "阿甘、阿國和阿強", "阿甘、阿信和阿強", "阿國、阿信和阿妹"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:19+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a995a09c8dd5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "214c7af8bde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "512", "s": "0505", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00945', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-110-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '假如蘋果是柳橙的替代品，則蘋果相對於柳橙的交叉價格彈性是：', '["負的", "正的", "零", "不一定"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:19+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a995a09c8dd5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "214c7af8bde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "512", "s": "0505", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00946', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-110-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設A國蘋果市場的均衡交易量為100公噸，現在因價格處在失衡狀態導致交易量為80公噸，如果交易 量由80公噸增加到90公噸，則蘋果市場的：', '["消費者剩餘下降", "生產者剩餘下降", "社會福利下降", "價格下降"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:19+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a995a09c8dd5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "214c7af8bde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "512", "s": "0505", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00947', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-110-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', 'LED燈具因技術進步使得生產成本下降，同時LED燈具省電效果佳使得消費者購買意願提升。我們可以 根據以上市場條件變動預測LED燈具市場的：', '["均衡價格一定上漲", "均衡價格一定下跌", "均衡交易量一定上升", "均衡交易量一定下降"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:19+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a995a09c8dd5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "214c7af8bde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "512", "s": "0505", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-00948', 'elementary-0a2fc18c', 'elementary-0a2fc18c-moex-110-2b7ba743', 'sub-elementary-0a2fc18c-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲每次去夜市買燒酒螺，無論價格如何變動，她一定購買200元，表示甲對燒酒螺的需求彈性絕對值為：', '["0", "1/200", "1", "200"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:19+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a995a09c8dd5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "214c7af8bde3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "512", "s": "0505", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "經濟學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
